'''卡西姆·蘇萊曼尼'''（{{lang-fa|قاسم سلیمانی}}，拉丁化：Qasem Soleimani，{{bd|1957年|3月11日|2020年|1月3日|catIdx=Soleimani}}<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=Iraqi TV Reports Strike Kills Powerful Iranian Revolutionary Guard Commander|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/02/world/middleeast/qassem-soleimani-iraq-iran-attack.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-01-02|accessdate=2020-01-03|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Falih|last=Hassan|first2=Alissa J.|last2=Rubin|first3=Michael|last3=Crowley|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200103022034/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/02/world/middleeast/qassem-soleimani-iraq-iran-attack.html|archive-date=2020-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是[[伊朗|伊朗]][[伊斯兰革命卫队|伊斯兰革命卫队]]少将，自1998年起至2020年擔任[[聖城軍|聖城軍]]的指揮官<ref name="online.wsj.com">{{cite web|url=http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303816504577305742884577460|title=Iran's Spymaster Soleimani Counters U.S. Moves in the Mideast - WSJ|date=2012-04-06|work=WSJ|access-date=2016-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022123935/http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303816504577305742884577460|archive-date=2014-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年晉升[[少將|革命卫队少将]]军衔<ref name=alfonehmar11>{{cite journal|last=Alfoneh|first=Ali|title=Iran’s Secret Network: Major General Qassem Suleimani’s Inner Circle|journal=Middle Eastern Outlooks|date=March 2011|volume=2|url=http://www.aei.org/files/2011/03/03/MEO-2011-03-No-2-g.pdf|accessdate=2013-02-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724182439/http://www.aei.org/files/2011/03/03/MEO-2011-03-No-2-g.pdf|archivedate=2012-07-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sarajevotimes.com/assertion-iranian-general-qassem-soleimani-was-in-bosnia-herzegovina-during-the-war|title=Assertion: Iranian general Qassem Soleimani was in Bosnia-Herzegovina during the War|date=2020-01-08|accessdate=2020-08-19|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205111828/https://www.sarajevotimes.com/assertion-iranian-general-qassem-soleimani-was-in-bosnia-herzegovina-during-the-war/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Donald Trump kills General Qasem Soleimani |url=https://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/business/work/donald-trump-orders-killing-of-iran-revolutionary-guard-chief-general-qasem-soleimani/news-story/ebb2787cf9448ce7ee362f0466fc7623 |accessdate=8 January 2020 |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph_(Sydney)|The Daily Telegraph (Sydney)]] |quote=General Soleimani was a U.S.-designated terrorist}}</ref>，主要负责境外军事和秘密行动。在他的晚年，他被部分人认为是伊朗僅次於[[阿里·哈梅内伊|哈梅内伊]]的人物<ref>{{cite news |last1=Rikar Hussein |last2=Mehdi Jedinia |title=Factbox: Iran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps |url=https://www.voanews.com/extremism-watch/factbox-irans-islamic-revolutionary-guard-corps |accessdate=8 January 2020 |work=[[Voice_of_America|Voice of America]] |date=8 April 2019 |quote=The United Nations and the European Union have refrained from designating the IRGC as a terror entity but have blacklisted key individuals of the force, including its leader Qasem Soleimani |archive-date=2020-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111030211/https://www.voanews.com/extremism-watch/factbox-irans-islamic-revolutionary-guard-corps |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Ali H. M. Abo Rezeg |title=PROFILE—Who is Qasem Soleimani? |url=https://www.aa.com.tr/en/middle-east/profile-who-is-qasem-soleimani-/1690827 |accessdate=8 January 2020 |work=Anadolu Agency |date=3 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200104171212/https://www.aa.com.tr/en/middle-east/profile-who-is-qasem-soleimani-/1690827 |archivedate=2020-01-04 |quote=Soleimani was declared a "terrorist and supporter of terrorism" by the U.S. He was among the Iranian individuals who were sanctioned by the UN Security Council resolution 1747 [...] on June 24, 2011, an official statement by the European Union said that European sanctions were imposed on three Iranian commanders of the Revolutionary Guards including Soleimani |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="newsweek" /><ref name="fox" /><ref name="rfi" /><ref name="daily" />。2020年，美军无人机在[[伊拉克|伊拉克]][[巴格达国际机场|巴格达国际机场]]附近[[2020年巴格达国际机场空袭|发动空袭]]將他刺杀身亡。在他死亡之后，伊朗政府追晋他为所谓“[[中将|革命卫队中将]]”军衔。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-50995792 |title=Qasem Soleimani: Blasts hit Baghdad area as Iraqis mourn Iranian general |publisher=BBC |date=2020-01-05 |access-date=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106224535/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-50995792 |archive-date=2020-01-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
蘇萊曼尼在[[克爾曼省|克爾曼省]]{{Link-en|拉波爾縣|Rabor County}}出生，父母是農民。13歲时，他为了償還父亲的債務而搬到城市里成为建筑工人。18岁的苏莱曼尼成为了一名水利建筑承包商，閑時会到健身房锻炼，也会去聆听[[鲁霍拉·穆萨维·霍梅尼|霍梅尼]]一个学徒的说道。

他有六名兄弟姐妹和两子两女。

=== 軍事生涯 ===
1979年[[伊朗伊斯兰革命|伊朗伊斯兰革命]]成功後，蘇萊曼尼加入新建的革命衛隊，並在[[兩伊戰爭|兩伊戰爭]]中作戰。<ref name=people20150327/>

在[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]中，蘇萊曼尼協調親伊朗[[民兵|民兵]]幫助[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]政府對抗反政府武裝，並參與策劃和指揮軍事行動。有前美國官員認為巴沙爾政府得以存在至今，蘇萊曼尼功不可沒。<ref name=people20150327/>

[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]攻佔[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]北部大片土地後，蘇萊曼尼於2014－15年協助指揮伊拉克政府聯同[[人民動員|人民動員]]進行的反擊[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]軍事行動。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2015/Mar-05/289654-from-the-east-iran-backed-force-advances-on-tikrit.ashx|title=From the east, Iran-backed force advances on Tikrit|work=The Daily Star|accessdate=2015-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403004100/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2015/Mar-05/289654-from-the-east-iran-backed-force-advances-on-tikrit.ashx|archive-date=2015-04-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[File:Qasem_Soleimani_received_Zolfaghar_Order_from_Ali_Khamenei_2.jpg|right]]

蘇萊曼尼曾被西方媒體認為是當時中東地區最有影響力的戰地指揮官和軍事戰略家。<ref name=people20150327>{{Cite news |url=http://gd.people.com.cn/GB/n/2015/0327/c123932-24299038.html |title=揭秘中东“谍王”苏莱曼尼 |website=人民網 |date=2015-03-27 |access-date=2016-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013221210/http://gd.people.com.cn/GB/n/2015/0327/c123932-24299038.html |archive-date=2016-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在伊朗於中东地区和美国的外交政策上有巨大的影响力，<ref>[https://www.aljazeera.com/amp/news/2020/01/qassem-soleimani-iran-elite-quds-force-leader-200103033905377.html -{“Who was Qassem Soleimani, Iran's IRGC's Quds Force leader?”}-] {{Wayback|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/amp/news/2020/01/qassem-soleimani-iran-elite-quds-force-leader-200103033905377.html |date=20200103151824 }} Al Jazeera [2020-01-03]</ref>更被外界廣泛認為是伊朗第二最有權勢的人，比起民選的[[伊朗總統|伊朗總統]]有更大權勢。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-50982193 |title=美国击毙伊朗军事指挥官 德黑兰誓言将“严重报复” |publisher=BBC |date=2020-01-04 |access-date=2020-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200105010955/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-50982193 |archive-date=2020-01-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

苏莱曼尼在伊朗及其中东的什叶派盟友中具有近乎神话般的地位。《时代》杂志评选他为2017年[[时代百大人物|100位最具影响力人物]]之一，形容他为一位将虚构传奇特工「007」[[詹姆斯·邦德|詹姆斯·邦德]]、二战德军元帥[[埃尔温·隆美尔|埃尔温·隆美尔]]与当代歌星[[女神卡卡|女神卡卡]]的特点集于一身的人物。<ref name=voa5231350>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/US-Iran-Soleimani-20200103/5231350.html |title=苏莱曼尼--伊朗中东扩张战略的策划者 |publisher=VOA |date=2020-01-04 |access-date=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200104045530/https://www.voachinese.com/a/US-Iran-Soleimani-20200103/5231350.html |archive-date=2020-01-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://time.com/collection/2017-time-100/4736337/qasem-soleimani/ |title=Major General Qasem Soleimani |access-date=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107024446/https://time.com/collection/2017-time-100/4736337/qasem-soleimani/ |archive-date=2020-01-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

美國在2005年認為他支持恐怖主義組織，將他列入恐怖主義份子名單<ref name="fox">{{cite news |last1=Jennifer Griffin |last2=Lucas Tomlinson |title=Exclusive: Quds Force commander Soleimani visited Moscow, met Russian leaders in defiance of sanctions |url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/exclusive-quds-force-commander-soleimani-visited-moscow-met-russian-leaders-in-defiance-of-sanctions |accessdate=8 January 2020 |work=Fox |date=6 August 2015 |quote=Soleimani was first designated a terrorist and sanctioned by the U.S. in 2005 for his role as a supporter of terrorism |archive-date=2020-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200108184618/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/exclusive-quds-force-commander-soleimani-visited-moscow-met-russian-leaders-in-defiance-of-sanctions |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年聯合國安理會通過[[联合国安理会1747号决议|1747號決議]]，制裁伊朗的濃縮鈾計劃，在附件中，將蘇萊曼尼列為制裁對象列表中，對他發布國際旅行禁令<ref name="daily">{{Cite news |url=https://www.dailysignal.com/2020/01/04/5-things-to-know-about-top-iranian-general-killed-by-us-airstrike/ |title=5 Things to Know About Top Iranian General Killed by US Airstrike |date=2020-01-04 |author=Fred Lucas |publisher=Daily Signal |access-date=2020-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127114335/https://www.dailysignal.com/2020/01/04/5-things-to-know-about-top-iranian-general-killed-by-us-airstrike/ |archive-date=2021-01-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國國務院發言人[[摩根·奥塔格斯|摩根·奥塔格斯]]稱他列名在聯合國安理會的恐怖份子名單中<ref>{{cite news |title=曾经的合作伙伴 苏莱马尼如今怎就成美国“眼中钉”“肉中刺”？ |url=http://news.cctv.com/2020/01/08/ARTIFODSf3VsU5Op3fxKgBA7200108.shtml |accessdate=2021-11-18 |work=CCTV |archive-date=2021-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211118011309/http://news.cctv.com/2020/01/08/ARTIFODSf3VsU5Op3fxKgBA7200108.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=苏莱马尼是联合国认定的恐怖分子？美国务院发言人信口雌黄被打脸 |url=https://v.cctv.com/2020/01/11/VIDE1LY3dIBiIVrV6IZAZYKG200111.shtml |accessdate=2021-11-18 |work=v.cctv.com |archive-date=2021-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211118011322/https://v.cctv.com/2020/01/11/VIDE1LY3dIBiIVrV6IZAZYKG200111.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國歐巴馬政府時期，認定他曾涉入策劃多次在美國[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]暗殺[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]駐美國大使的事件，在2011年將他列入恐怖份子名單<ref name="newsweek">"In 2011, the Obama administration sanctioned Soleimani for an alleged plot to assassinate the Saudi ambassador to the U.S. in Washington, D.C." https://www.newsweek.com/donald-trump-barack-obama-designated-qassem-soleimani-terrorist-iran-did-nothing-1480771 {{Wayback|url=https://www.newsweek.com/donald-trump-barack-obama-designated-qassem-soleimani-terrorist-iran-did-nothing-1480771 |date=20200108200154 }}</ref>。[[法国国际广播电台|法国国际广播电台]]引述網站伊朗外交的內容，因為涉嫌策劃暗殺沙烏地阿拉伯駐美大使，蘇萊曼尼在2007年曾被列入聯合國反恐名單<ref name="rfi">{{Cite web |url=http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%9C/20200105-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%8B%8F%E8%8E%B1%E6%9B%BC%E5%B0%BC%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA2007%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%BB%E8%BA%AB%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95 |title=伊朗苏莱曼尼兄弟二人2007年跻身联合国反恐黑名单 |access-date=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106030946/http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%9C/20200105-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%8B%8F%E8%8E%B1%E6%9B%BC%E5%B0%BC%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA2007%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%BB%E8%BA%AB%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95 |archive-date=2020-01-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 死亡 ===
{{See also|2020年巴格达国际机场空袭}}
2020年1月3日，一架美国[[MQ-9收割者侦察机|MQ-9“收割者”无人机]]在伊拉克[[巴格達國際機場|巴格达国际机场]]附近向苏莱曼尼的车队发起攻击，苏莱曼尼死于[[2020年巴格达国际机场空袭|空袭]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name=bbc50979463/>。一同丧生的还有伊拉克[[人民動員|人民動員]]部隊副指揮官[[阿布·马赫迪·穆罕迪斯|阿布·马赫迪·穆罕迪斯]]。同一天，伊朗追授蘇萊曼尼為中將，最高領袖[[阿里·哈梅內伊|阿里·哈梅內伊]]宣布全國哀悼3日，並宣稱發動襲擊的「罪犯」將會面臨嚴厲報復，又任命[[伊斯梅爾·賈尼|伊斯梅爾·賈尼]]为苏莱曼尼的继任人。<ref name=bbc50979463>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-50979463 |title=Qasem Soleimani: US kills top Iranian general in Baghdad air strike |publisher=BBC |date=2020-01-03 |access-date=2020-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200103025417/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-50979463 |archive-date=2020-01-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[https://www.reuters.com/article/us-iraq-security-blast-iran-successor/iran-names-deputy-quds-force-commander-to-replace-soleimani-after-killing-idUSKBN1Z20X4 -{“Iran names deputy Quds Force commander to replace Soleimani after killing”}-] {{Wayback|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-iraq-security-blast-iran-successor/iran-names-deputy-quds-force-commander-to-replace-soleimani-after-killing-idUSKBN1Z20X4 |date=20200106061249 }} Reuters [2020-01-03]</ref>美國總統[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]對蘇萊曼尼之死表示祝贺，他说苏莱曼尼需要為数以千計美国人、伊拉克人和伊朗人的死亡负责。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-hails-death-of-irans-most-influential-general-20200103/5231501.html |title=伊朗重要将领在美军空袭中丧生 特朗普总统表示庆贺 |publisher=VOA |date=2020-01-04 |access-date=2020-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200104073543/https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-hails-death-of-irans-most-influential-general-20200103/5231501.html |archive-date=2020-01-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>伊朗国内对苏莱曼尼的死讯反应激烈，有官员和学界人士在媒体上表现激动；民众在社交媒体上发表哀悼文和反美言论。<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/world-europe-50981734 “Defiant Iranians mourn 'martyr' Soleimani”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/world-europe-50981734 |date=20200103153612 }} BBC [03-01-2020]</ref>

[[File:Demonstrations_in_Iran_over_the_death_of_Qasem_Soleimani.jpg|right]]
據伊拉克看守政府總理[[阿卜杜勒-迈赫迪|阿卜杜勒-迈赫迪]]表示，苏莱曼尼來伊拉克的目的是與自己會面，但美国在距离会见还有几个小时的时候杀死了苏莱曼尼<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.ckxx.net/guoji/p/203694.html |title=伊拉克总理：苏莱曼尼为缓和与沙特关系而来 “被杀当天原本要见我 |access-date=2020-01-06 |archive-date=2020-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714152401/http://m.ckxx.net/guoji/p/203694.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

美國總統[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]表示，殺死蘇萊曼尼的動機是因為他密謀炸毀美國大使館<ref>{{cite news |title=特朗普谈美为何击杀苏莱曼尼：他密谋炸毁大使馆 |url=https://m.chinanews.com/wap/detail/zw/gj/2020/01-10/9056059.shtml |agency=中國新聞網 |accessdate=2020-01-14 |archive-date=2020-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714152420/https://m.chinanews.com/wap/detail/zw/gj/2020/01-10/9056059.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《叙利亚圣战》（The Syrian Jihad）一书的作者查尔斯·李斯特（Charles Lister）認為苏莱曼尼被杀在战略意义和影响方面远远超过了「[[蓋達組織|基地]]」组织首领[[奥萨马·本·拉登|奥萨马·本·拉登]]或「[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]」首领[[阿布·贝克尔·巴格达迪|阿布·贝克尔·巴格达迪]]之死。李斯特說這件事讓美國與伊朗的敵對大幅升級，此前[[以色列|以色列]]就是因为担心杀死苏莱曼尼的后果而一再放弃除掉他的机会。李斯特認為苏莱曼尼之死将给伊朗在本地区的图谋造成重大损失。<ref name=voa5231350/>

=== 丧礼 === 
[[File:_Qasem_Soleim_funeral_Tehran_7.jpg|right]]

苏莱曼尼普遍在国内被视为烈士，媒体指他是继[[鲁霍拉·穆萨维·霍梅尼|鲁霍拉·穆萨维·霍梅尼]]后首位擁有多场丧礼荣誉的伊朗人。<ref>[https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/443869/Farewell-Commander “Farewell, Commander”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/443869/Farewell-Commander |date=20200107182842 }} Tehran Times [06-01-2020]</ref>1月4日，伊拉克民众在巴格达为他举行丧礼游行并高叫反美和反以色列的口号。<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2020/jan/04/thousands-of-mourners-march-in-suleimani-funeral-procession-video “Thousands march in Baghdad funeral procession for Qassem Suleimani – video”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2020/jan/04/thousands-of-mourners-march-in-suleimani-funeral-procession-video |date=20200106082502 }} The Guardian [04-01-2020]</ref>游行的起点是[[卡济米耶清真寺|卡济米耶清真寺]]，伊拉克总理[[阿迪勒·阿卜杜勒-迈赫迪|阿迪勒·阿卜杜勒-迈赫迪]]也在场。苏莱曼尼的遺體先后被带到[[什叶派|什叶派]]圣城[[卡爾巴拉|卡爾巴拉]]和[[納杰夫|納杰夫]]。

1月5日，多名身穿黑衣服装的伊朗民众在[[馬什哈德|馬什哈德]]和[[阿瓦士|阿瓦士]]上街游行，悼念苏莱曼尼。有一些激烈的人以流泪和拍打胸口表示哀悼。<ref>[https://www.dawn.com/news/1526444 “Qasem Soleimani's body returned to Iran”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1526444 |date=20200106050804 }} Dawn [05-01-2020]</ref>
[[File:Qasem_Soleimani_funeral_2.jpg|left]]
6日，伊朗在首都德黑兰为苏莱曼尼举行正式的丧礼。多名出席的民众再次高叫反美口号。<ref>[https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-51004688 “Soleimani: Huge crowds pack Tehran for commander's funeral”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-51004688 |date=20200106070558 }} BBC [06-01-2020]</ref>最高领袖阿里·哈梅內伊亲自主导祈祷，而苏莱曼尼的女兒对民众表示美军的家人將會为他的死付出代价。<ref>[https://www.cbsnews.com/news/ayatollah-ali-khamenei-irans-supreme-leader-weeps-casket-general-soleimani-today-2020-01-06/ “Iran's supreme leader weeps over casket of slain top general”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/ayatollah-ali-khamenei-irans-supreme-leader-weeps-casket-general-soleimani-today-2020-01-06/ |date=20200106122720 }} CBS News [06-01-2020]</ref>媒体也拍到哈梅内伊在丧礼上流泪的画面，评论称這顯示了哈梅内伊和苏莱曼尼的亲密关系。<ref>[https://news.sky.com/video/irans-supreme-leader-cries-at-soleimani-prayers-11902137 “Iran's supreme leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei cries at Soleimani prayers”] {{Wayback|url=https://news.sky.com/video/irans-supreme-leader-cries-at-soleimani-prayers-11902137 |date=20210801115709 }} Sky News [06-01-2020]</ref><ref>[https://www.nzherald.co.nz/world/news/article.cfm?c_id=2&objectid=12298448 “Iran's leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei cries at funeral of slain General Qassem Soleimani”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/world/news/article.cfm?c_id=2&objectid=12298448 |date=20200108071514 }} NZ Herald [07-01-2020]</ref><ref>[https://apnews.com/14792cc1d7f73ffec8f8c425b73b44fb “Iranian leader’s tears a sign of respect for slain general”] {{Wayback|url=https://apnews.com/14792cc1d7f73ffec8f8c425b73b44fb |date=20200107162722 }} Associated Press [06-01-2020]</ref>伊拉克什葉派穆斯林的領袖之一[[穆克塔达·萨德尔|穆克塔达·萨德尔]]到访苏莱曼尼家中，向他的家人表示慰问。1月7日，蘇萊曼尼在其家乡[[克尔曼|克尔曼]]下葬<ref>{{cite news |title=苏莱曼尼的遗体被运抵伊朗 |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/THE-BODY-OF-GENERAL-QASSEM-SOLEIMANI-HAS-ARRIVED-IN-IRAN-20200105/5232679.html |agency=美國之音 |accessdate=2020-01-06 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205025641/https://www.voachinese.com/a/THE-BODY-OF-GENERAL-QASSEM-SOLEIMANI-HAS-ARRIVED-IN-IRAN-20200105/5232679.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但送葬队伍发生[[卡西姆·蘇萊曼尼葬禮|踩踏意外]]，造成56人死亡，213人受伤<ref>{{cite news|title=伊朗踩踏事件死亡人数升至56人|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-01/08/c_1125432906.htm|publisher=新華網|date=2020-01-08|accessdate=2020-01-08|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812191342/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-01/08/c_1125432906.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
